\f0\b\fs15 \cf0 Run Template Queries\ \pard\pardeftab720\qj
\b0 \cf0 Dozens of useful queries have been predefined. These range from simple queries to retrieve a particular type of data to more complex queries that span the different types of data. You can create your own templates if you log in. Search for templates on the templates page or on each category page.\ \ \pard\pardeftab720\qj
\b \cf0 Use the FlyMine QueryBuilder \b0 \ Advanced users can use a flexible query interface to construct their own data mining queries across the multiple integrated data sources, to modify existing template queries or to create new template queries.\ \
\b Query and Analyse Lists of Data \b0 \ All queries in FlyMine can be performed on lists which can be uploaded or saved from query results. You can merge, subtract and find common members if you have more than one list. All lists are automatically analyzed.\ \pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\qj\pardirnatural \cf0 \
\b Personal Account\ \pard\pardeftab720\qj
\b0 \cf0 If you log in, you can save all your lists and queries permanently in MyMine. To create an account you just need to supply an email adress. All of your data is kept private.}
